// Additional content
.card 
    .card-header.pb-0
        +card-header('Additional content', '','','Use the', '.alert , .bg-light-*', ' utility class to quickly provide additional content within any alerts.')
    .card-body.dark-alert
        .alert.bg-light-primary.default-border(role='alert')
            h5.alert-heading.pb-2 Please! Check your notifications
            p
                | The duty of notification is imposed upon the head of the family, and also upon the medical practitioner who may be in attendance on the patient.
            hr
            p.mb-0 The emergency notification system is free and is available in all 50 states.
        .alert.bg-light-secondary.default-border(role='alert')
            h5.alert-heading.pb-2 Something went wrong! Please, chrome update.
            p
                | The duty of notification is imposed upon the head of the family, and also upon the medical practitioner who may be in attendance on the patient.
            hr
            p.mb-0
                | Whenever you need to, be sure to use margin utilities to keep things nice and tidy.
        .alert.bg-light-tertiary.mb-0.default-border(role='alert')
            h5.alert-heading.pb-2 Please! Hidden cameras were not installed.
            p
                | Due to increasingly accessible technology, hidden cameras have grown in popularity among regular people in recent years.
            hr
            p.mb-0
                | Consider moving clocks and plush animals from your area if you think they may be concealing cameras because they are both portable items.

